            <div class="reviews-grid">
                <div class="card text-center mb-5">
                    <span class="name">Karim S.</span>
                    <small class="text-black-50 font-weight-bold">Tripadvisor.com, Egypt</small>
                    <div class="location mt-4">
                        <p class="txt2">Second time to visit and definitely won't be the last…in fact service and
                            overall
                            experience got better since last visited two years ago, not to mention the marvelous
                            view…the hotel
                            is an excellent getaway for couples…highly recommended</p>
                        <div class="carda p-3">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
