                    <span class="name">Sara N.</span>
                    <small class="text-black-50 font-weight-bold">Expedia.com, Germany</small>
                    <div class="location mt-4">
                        <p class="txt2">Two nights at Basma Hotel were like heaven. The room with a balcony was spacious
                            and
                            comfortable. The staff was helpful and friendly. The location was perfect. Atmosphere
